{"tid":864390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你殺左我啦","createTime":"2018-10-16T07:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T10:06:26.000Z","uid":205191,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c4a3c93bd4d2872f4e6dd4710a3da307d41ffc2","tid":864390,"uid":205191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"12年前被父母拋棄到香港（利申香港出世）<br />\n仲記得果時係2006年9月<br />\n之後2007年2月有人收養我<br />\n到左而家18歲收養期結束<br />\n自己一個係hall度住<br />\n日唸夜唸點解自己會咁不幸<br />\n明明繼父月賺20萬人民幣<br />\n1%都唔分比我<br />\n而家D大陸人真係咁哀<br />\n阿媽咁鐘意搞婚外情<br />\n不如唔好生我出黎啦<br />\n係世上受苦<br />\n過住孤兒仔既生活<br />\n不如你殺左我啦。"},{"pid":"c21a2a2415730a151b608f2d5f018b147e54348d","tid":864390,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"孤兒仔通常好捱得。"},{"pid":"5805fb7281b375d64d0bc2492af793c6283b29cc","tid":864390,"uid":205191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21a2a2415730a151b608f2d5f018b147e54348d","tid":864390,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"孤兒仔通常好捱得。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"表面捱得<br />\n但精神就。。。<br />\n成日喊，成日思考人生既意義"},{"pid":"b028b7cb3a55fedc04d60b5c62db42d0630b48c7","tid":864390,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"我唔係孤兒我唔明<br />\n但呢個世界你睇我好我睇你好<br />\n當係為咗自己而活<br />\n俾個好嘅人生自己<br />\n無人無物可以唔洗就住就住<br />\n有咩想做就想，想博想試就放膽去<br />\n當然，犯法的事除外<br />\n過一個屬於自己而又無憾的人生<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c232084859b311e13775ab1ea785f83defb1338","tid":864390,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:51:16.000Z","msg":"所以話人生在世無一個靠得住，最好就係自己，好彩你仲有hall住，第時出到黎社會自私d，搵到錢益晒自己，世界上無人信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e683f35e1309517fe15a578b1b84eaff86521ffe","tid":864390,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"同我拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhehe"},{"pid":"4f629dae5682f2553a8e12fdae25e38d44ea4fd0","tid":864390,"uid":205191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e683f35e1309517fe15a578b1b84eaff86521ffe","tid":864390,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"同我拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhehe"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"no"}]}